			  	You mean something along these lines? <br />
<br />
Weapon effects:<br />
Shield Piercing - chance of doubling the damage dealt to shields<br />
Shield Overheat - triples the damage dealt to shields<br />
Shield Distortion - chance of bypassing the shields completly<br />
Armor Piercing - chance of Critical Hit (double damage to ship hull)<br />
Additional Damage to Bio Armor - self-explanatory<br />
			   <P align=right></P>
